---
import BaseLayout from '../../src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Seller AI HQ" description="Why Seller AI HQ exists and who it helps.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="pill">About</div>
      <h1 style="font-size:42px; margin-bottom:14px;">Built for sellers who want useful AI, not hype.</h1>
      <p class="top">
        Seller AI HQ exists to help online sellers find practical AI tools for listings, content, visuals, and growth.
        We focus on usefulness, speed, and real workflows instead of noisy generic directories.
      </p>
      <p class="top">
        The long-term goal is simple: become a trusted resource for lean seller stacks, AI-assisted workflows,
        and tool recommendations that actually save time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
